          "description": "I love DDS Group. They are always time efficient when it comes to wait time, making appointments, and always ensuring they will get down to the problem when it comes to their patients teeth.\n\nMs. Lydia is the receptionist for DDS Group. She is amazing and cares about the patients in the office, doing her best to qualify appointments for patients. She is easy and fun to talk to as well.\n\nMs. Krina is a dentist that focuses on cleaning patient's teeth. She is very good at the cleanings and lets the patients know if they have to floss more and brush better. I recommend having her cleaning my teeth!\n\nLastly, Dr. Bader I love her! She is a dentist that fills in cavities and she is the best at what she does. She makes sure her patients are comfortable and she knows what she's doing. When I had to get a crown, she shaved down my tooth perfectly and I was super comfortable when she was doing my teeth. Love her down :)",
